quran[63]{c,v,t}:
  76,19,"Bazaba bazengurukwamo n’abana b’abahungu bahoraho (badasaza cyangwa ngo bapfe, babaha amafunguro), ubabonye wagira ngo ni inigi zishashagirana (Lu’ulu’u) zanyanyagijwe"
  76,20,Kandi nunarebayo (mu Ijuru) uzabona ingabire (zitagereranywa) ndetse n’ubwami buhebuje
  76,21,Bazaba bambaye imyambaro y’icyatsi kibisi ikoze mu ihariri yorohereye n’iremereye. Bazanambikirwamo ibikomo bya Feza kandi Nyagasani wabo azabaha ikinyobwa gisukuye
  76,22,"(Bazanabwirwa bati) “Mu by’ukuri ibi ni ibihembo byanyu, kandi umuhate wanyu warakiriwe.”"
  76,23,Mu by’ukuri (yewe Muhamadi) ni twe twaguhishuriye Qur’an mu byiciro
  76,24,"Bityo, ihanganire itegeko rya Nyagasani wawe, kandi ntuzumvire umunyabyaha cyangwa umuhakanyi muri bo"
  76,25,Kandi ujye usingiza izina rya Nyagasani wawe mu gitondo no ku gicamunsi
  76,26,Na nijoro umwubamire kandi unamusingize igihe kirekire mu ijoro
  76,27,"Mu by’ukuri abo (bahakanyi) bakunda ubuzima bwo ku isi butaramba, bakirengagiza umunsi uremereye (w’ibihano)"
  76,28,Ni twe twabaremye dukomeza ingingo zabo. Kandi tubishatse twabasimbuza abandi bameze nka bo
  76,29,"Mu by’ukuri iyi (mirongo ya Qur’an) ni urwibutso, bityo ushaka nayoboke inzira imuganisha kwa Nyagasani we"
  76,30,"Kandi nta cyo mwashaka (ngo mukigereho) keretse Allah abishatse. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  76,31,Yinjiza mu mpuhwe ze uwo ashaka. Naho inkozi z’ibibi yaziteguriye ibihano bibabaza
  77,1,Ndahiye imiyaga yoherezwa ikurikiranye
  77,2,N’imiyaga y’inkubi
  77,3,N’imiyaga ikwirakwiza ibicu n’imvura
  77,4,N’(imirongo ya Qur’an) itandukanya ukuri n’ikinyoma
  77,5,N’abamalayika bazanira amahishurirwa (intumwa za Allah)
  77,6,Kugira ngo avaneho urwitwazo cyangwa kugira ngo aburire
  77,7,Mu by’ukuri ibyo musezeranywa bizasohora
  77,8,Igihe inyenyeri zizakurwaho (urumuri rwazo rukazima)
  77,9,N’igihe ikirere kizasandazwa
  77,10,N’igihe imisozi izariturwa igatumuka nk’ivumbi
  77,11,N’igihe intumwa zizakoranyirizwa hamwe ku gihe cyagenwe (kugira ngo zitange ubuhamya ku bo zatumweho)
  77,12,Ni uwuhe munsi (ibyo byose) byarindirijwe
  77,13,Ni ku munsi w’urubanza (ubwo Allah azakiranura ibiremwa)
  77,14,Ni iki cyakumenyesha umunsi w’urubanza icyo uzaba uri cyo
  77,15,"Kuri uwo munsi (w’izuka), ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyuraga (uwo munsi)"
  77,16,Ese ntitworetse abo hambere
  77,17,Nuko tukabakurikiza abo hanyuma
  77,18,Uko ni ko tugenza inkozi z’ibibi
  77,19,"Kuri uwo munsi (w’izuka), ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyuraga (uwo munsi)"
  77,20,Ese ntitwabaremye mu mazi aciriritse
  77,21,Nuko tukayashyira mu cyicaro gitekanye (nyababyeyi)
  77,22,Kugeza igihe kizwi
  77,23,Nuko tukagena (imikurire y’umwana n’ivuka rye) kandi ni twe duhebuje mu kugena
  77,24,"Kuri uwo munsi (w’izuka), ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyuraga (uwo munsi)"
  77,25,Ese isi ntitwayigize ihuriro
  77,26,Ry’abazima (bayituyeho) n’abapfuye (bayishyinguwemo)
  77,27,"Hanyuma tukanayishyiramo imisozi miremire, ndetse tukabaha n’amazi y’urubogobogo"
  77,28,"Kuri uwo munsi (w’izuka), ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyuraga (uwo munsi)"
  77,29,(Abahakanyi bazabwirwa bati) “Ngaho nimujye aho mwajyaga muhinyura (mu muriro wa Jahanamu)!”
  77,30,“Ngaho nimujye mu gicucu (cy’umwotsi wa Jahanamu) kigabanyijemo amashami atatu”
  77,31,“Nta bwugamo gitanga ndetse nta n’ubwo kirinda ikibatsi cy’umuriro”
  77,32,Mu by’ukuri (uwo muriro) utera ibishashi bingana n’inyubako nini
  77,33,(Ibyo bishashi) bimeze nk’ingamiya z’amagaju
  77,34,"Kuri uwo munsi (w’izuka), ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyuraga (uwo munsi)"
  77,35,"Kuri uwo munsi, nta cyo bazaba bashobora kuvuga"
  77,36,Nta n’uburenganzira bazahabwa bwo kugira urwitwazo batanga
  77,37,"Kuri uwo munsi (w’izuka), ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyuraga (uwo munsi)"
  77,38,"Uwo uzaba ari umunsi w’urubanza, ubwo (mwe) n’abo hambere, tuzaba twabakoranyirije hamwe"
  77,39,"Niba hari amayeri mufite (yo guhunga ibihano byanjye), ngaho nimuyankorere"
  77,40,"Kuri uwo munsi (w’izuka), ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyuraga (uwo munsi)"
  77,41,"Mu by’ukuri abagandukira (Allah), (ku munsi w’imperuka) bazaba bari hagati y’ibicucu (by’ibiti byo mu ijuru) ndetse n’amasoko (atemba)"
  77,42,(Bazaba bahabwamo) n’imbuto (z’amoko anyuranye) bazajya bifuza
  77,43,"(Bazabwirwa bati) “Nimurye, munywe kandi mugubwe neza kubera ibyo mwajyaga mukora.”"
  77,44,Mu by’ukuri uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza
  77,45,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,46,"(Yemwe bahakanyi) “Nimurye munishimishe by’igihe gito (mu buzima bwo ku isi), kuko rwose muri inkozi z’ibibi.”"
  77,47,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,48,N’iyo babwiwe bati “Nimwuname (musali)!” Ntabwo bunama (ngo basali)
  77,49,Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri ba bandi bahinyura (umunsi w’izuka)
  77,50,None se nyuma y’iyi (Qur’an) ni ayahe magambo yandi bazemera